ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T01:29:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>公司好細 基本上成撚日要同個好撚黑人憎既懶叻肥仔一齊放工<br />\n因為大家都行同一條路 好自然放工都會一齊行<br />\n但我實在愈黎愈頂條撚屌唔順<br />\n性格黑人憎把聲難聽不特止 仲要唔知點解硬係有種優越感係到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家又無共同話題 次次都係我格硬搵啲野出黎講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係頂唔順 有冇方法可以飛甩佢自己一個放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你話約左男友 佢即走</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢知我有男友啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但成日都一齊走 真係想喊出黎 放左工仲要應付啲閪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d884c36350be057cc7036837fc0c9cacb0bd6bff","tid":264503,"uid":18953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T01:30:05.000Z","msg":":唔好意思 我行先啦"},{"pid":"b2953494d73dd731bb1c1e99407d412446f97a6b","tid":264503,"uid":13952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T01:30:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>求其話約左人走先咪得囉</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n聽日試下 其實我日日都咁講佢係咪會醒水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68cddc063cf50aa40680e72c72533e95ced84468","tid":264503,"uid":13952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T01:31:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>煲電話粥唔理佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但如果一齊走既話咁樣好似好冇禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6baf161024f18ee32a91e9c76cec4acc185ab7ad","tid":264503,"uid":46595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T01:32:17.000Z","msg":"你新黎定佢新黎?<br />\n其實唔一齊走幾日就唔會KEEP住架啦<br />\n乜藉口都好 有野做 / 你走先 / 約左人 乜都得啦<br />\n你新手上班? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/s